metadata.title: Modway Origin 47" Mid-Century Modern Wood Coffee Table In Natural Gray
features: MID-CENTURY STYLE - Clean lines, rounded corners, and two-toned detail lend mid-century intrigue to this contemporary coffee table. Update your space with organic wood grain and retro charm
WOOD COFFEE TABLE - Sitting atop a frame with splayed legs, Origin has a durable particleboard construction and boasts a rich wood grain veneer complementing the solid color full-extension drawers
SPACIOUS STORAGE - An ideal addition to a living room, Origin's two spacious drawers offer concelead storage. Display and store books, pictures, home accessories on this versatile modern coffee table
COFFEE TABLE MEASUREMENTS - Complement contemporary, modern, mid-century, and farmhouse themed d√©cors with Origin. Dimensions: 23"L x 47"W x 14"H
description: Bring the iconic energy of mid-century style to your bedroom or guest suite with the Origin 47" Coffee Table. Crafted with durable fiberboard for reliable support, Origin comes with a splayed frame, rounded edges, linear design, wood grain veneer, and two full-extension drawers for concealed storage. The perfect complement to your living room decor, display and store magazines, books, pictures, home accessories, and favorite beverages on this contemporary coffee table.
